AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-cluster-with-serviceiprange-nodeLaunchConfiguration-59dd670
                          MinSize: 2
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-0a885f511dc96d4f7","subnet-0ee22d073386d2ea2","subnet-071ec8a4e737b9413"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-cluster-with-serviceiprange-eksCluster-a739dbd-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-cluster-with-serviceiprange-eksCluster-a739dbd
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
